\subsection{Method \code{get_spot_account_type()}}{
Get Spot Account Types

Retrieves the account types that have been opened for HF (High-Frequency)
spot trading. This indicates which account categories are active.
\subsection{Workflow}{
\enumerate{
\item \strong{Request}: Authenticated GET to the HF accounts opened endpoint.
\item \strong{Parsing}: If a named list is returned, converts to a single-row \code{data.table}.
If a list of entries is returned, row-binds into a multi-row \code{data.table}.
Returns an empty \code{data.table} if no accounts are opened.
}
}

\subsection{API Endpoint}{

\verb{GET https://api.kucoin.com/api/v1/hf/accounts/opened}
}

