\itemize{
\item \strong{Balance Checks}: Query available funds before placing orders to avoid insufficient balance errors.
\item \strong{Portfolio Snapshot}: Retrieve all account balances periodically for portfolio tracking and rebalancing.
\item \strong{Filter by Type}: Use \code{query = list(type = "trade")} to get only trading account balances for order sizing.
